Text:
Lissie - Why You Runnin\' [EP] - MP3@320kbps - GCJM

^ This is what can happen when you put an apostrophe in the title.  But you sure spelled the album right.

Just thought I'd point out its 262kbps (avg) VBR and NOT 320kbps.
Don't get me wrong the quality is fine but its not 320 as the title says.

@66677 - you just blew my mind O.o

You are absolutely correct.

I sincerely apologise for the mistaken labelling.
I don't know why that happened but I can assure you it was not intentional.

Please do enjoy the tunes.
